Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.74,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}このままでいっか なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:51.21,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}未來は未來の風が吹きそうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:57.82,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}はじまりの空は未完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.16,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}愛だ戀だなんだ今んとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:09.38,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}対岸のジェットコースター
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.98,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}頑張るより 頑張る人を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:15.45,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}応援するほうが得意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.97,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}フラット気味の目線の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:21.19,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}暴走狂のディスプレイ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.16,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}ドラマにならないリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.88,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}どう料理するの?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.00,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}キャラが弱いとか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:33.19,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}嫌な安心感があるだとか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:39.43,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}目立ちたいなんて一度も言ってないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.65,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}どうでもいいけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.20,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}このままでいっか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.82,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}どっか遠くの街も青空なら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:53.57,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}立ち止まる日もなんとなく楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.83,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}今はまだ原石の夢が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:16:00.20,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}いつか輝けるならいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.56,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}まぶしい!って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.76,megumi_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}いつかボヤきたい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.74,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}保持不變 也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.74,0:14:51.21,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}未來的風 似乎正吹向未來呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.21,0:14:57.82,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}序章的天空 尚未完成
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.16,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}戀愛諸事沒有多想
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.16,0:15:09.38,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}如同那對岸的雲霄飛車
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.98,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}比起自己努力
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.98,0:15:15.45,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}更擅長給大家鼓勁
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.97,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}毫無起伏的眼神
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.97,0:15:21.19,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}凝視著暴走的顯示器
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.16,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}沒有戲劇性的現實
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.88,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}該怎麼調味才好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.00,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}角色很薄弱嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.00,0:15:33.19,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}有種令人討厭的安心感嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.19,0:15:39.43,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}我可沒說過要引人注目哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.65,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}雖然怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.20,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}保持不變 也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.82,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}遠方的城鎮若是晴天
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.82,0:15:53.57,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}駐足眺望也很開心
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.83,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}尚在孵化的夢想
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.83,0:16:00.20,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}願能綻放耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.56,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}那奪目的光彩
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.76,megumi_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}真想親口說出來
